HEADWORD: Lutheran
<hw>Lu"ther*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to <etsep>Luther</etsep>; adhering to the
doctrines of Luther or the Lutheran Church.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

